description: COLUMBUS, Ohio (AP) — “Hillbilly Elegy” author JD Vance   won Ohio’s contentious and hyper-competitive  GOP Senate primary on Tuesday, buoyed by Donald Trump’s endorsement in a race that was an early test of the former president’s hold on his party as the midterm season  kicks into high gear.
